englishDefinition: to get somebody to do something

info: １ can also be read ワン. 壱, 弌 and 壹 are used in legal documents
with a verb in negative form
when counting aloud, usu. ひ or ひい

pronounciations.一昨年: いっさくねん, おととし

pronounciations.no kanji: チョット, ちょいと, チョッと

info: before a verb in negative form

pronounciations.天辺: てっぺん, てへん, てっぺい

info: often in てっぺんを回る or てっぺん回る
esp. 頂辺 when in kanji

seeAlso: 頂けない いただけない

pronounciations.頂点捕食者: ちょうてんほしょくしゃ

pronounciations.頂上会談: ちょうじょうかいだん

englishDefinition: general principle (as opposed to individual concrete phenomenon)
(in neo-Confucianism) the underlying principles of the cosmos
